      <bold class="bold">Climate Change Causes</bold>
     </td>
     <td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1" class="td">The global carbon dioxide (CO
      <sub class="sub">2</sub>) concentration in the atmosphere has increased during the past 250 years.
     </td>
